parameters: ストーリー　砦潜入
シシリア HK01-1
シシリア HK01-1
I made it out! ...Haa... Haa...! But...!\n< Cecilia >
Lady Cecilia?\n< Serena >
This isn't where I wanted to be...!\n< Cecilia >

This is the fort's main gate! But to get
out from this courtyard, we need a key!\n< Cecilia >

Well, there's no more guards or
anything! We could just climb over the
walls around here...!\n< Cecilia >

This thing... won't let us escape...
probably. Haa, Haa... damn, it caught
up...\n< Cecilia >

...Well... when you think about it, the
situation has become simpler.\n< Serena >

In other words, all we need to do is
defeat this creature right here.\n< Serena >
????: Maaaaaaaahhhhhhh!!!!

Considering that escaping from the
innermost part of that venue was the
hardest part.\n< Serena >

This... whatever it is... this monster
turning everything upside down might
actually be convenient for us.\n< Serena >
That's if we can win here...\n< Cecilia >
Lady Cecilia.\n< Serena >
Yes.\n< Cecilia >
I'm counting on your Splendor.\n< Serena >
Leave it to me.\n< Cecilia >

Now then. I have no idea who you are,
what you want, or what's going on.\n< Serena >
But I must get out of here.\n< Serena >
I'll shake you off right here.\n< Serena >
????: Maaaaaaaahhhhhhh!!!!

My name is Serena. Fuoco. R. Brillante.
D. La. Gratia.\n< Serena >

The god who illuminates this world! I
will take your life and grant you a
shameful death!\n< Serena >
Come at me if you dare!\n< Serena >
ストーリー　砦潜入　勝利
回想セーブ エンディング
シシリア HK01-1
シシリア HK01-1
"I've captured it. Your sound."\n< Serena >
"Haaah...!"\n< Serena >

"It took some time due to your soft
body... but as long as you have a
physical form, there's sound within it.
Waves. Rhythm."\n< Serena >

"I've captured that sound and 'dressed'
you in Apher-Bile."\n< Serena >

"You are enveloped in an armor of sound.
Resonating, reverberating, the bouncing
sound becomes a billion vibrations."\n< Serena >
"And vibration is, in essence, heat."\n< Serena >
"Guh...!"\n< Serena >
"It hurts...!"\n< Serena >
"Kuku...!"\n< Serena >
"My heat..."\n< Serena >
"In my Phorc...!"\n< Serena >
"Burn!"\n< Serena >
"Be consumed!"\n< Serena >
"What...?"\n< Serena >
"..."\n< Serena >
!動物-ユニコーン01-1
!動物-ユニコーン01-1
"Oh... ohh..."\n< Serena >
"Splendor..."\n< Serena >
"My brilliance..."\n< Serena >

"Splendor, as long as you are safe,
that alone... for me..."\n< Serena >
"Hey!"\n< Cecilia >

"Don't mess with me! Just now, with its
horn...!"\n< Cecilia >
"..."\n< Serena >
"It's alright, Cecilia-sama."\n< Serena >
"Nothing's alright!"\n< Cecilia >

"It can't be helped... It's their
nature. Splendor has done nothing
wrong."\n< Serena >

"All the evil lies within me. This child
is merely reacting to that ugliness."\n< Serena >
"..."\n< Cecilia >

"...Splendor. I'm sorry for making you
feel uncomfortable."\n< Serena >

"Just sleep a little longer... I'll take
you home soon..."\n< Serena >
!動物-ユニコーン01-1
this._pattern = 1; this._originalPattern = 1;
!動物-ユニコーン01-1
this._pattern = 1; this._originalPattern = 1;
"...Phew."\n< Serena >

"Ow, it hurts... Once I calm down, the
pain..."\n< Serena >

"This means... I might not be able to
play the piano anymore. I've just given
my father and mother another reason to
scold me."\n< Serena >
"...Serena."\n< Cecilia >

So then, Serena, for what purpose...?
Why did you work so hard for this? It's
just...\n< Cecilia >
It's too much...\n< Cecilia >

...I didn't come this far expecting any
reward.\n< Serena >

I simply wanted to repay the friendship.
Even if it's something that has already
passed.\n< Serena >

I made my decision and followed
through... That's why I'm satisfied.\n< Serena >
...I'm satisfied.\n< Serena >

Ah... Splendor...! The white fur on
your back that I've dreamed of...!\n< Serena >
I won't let go...! Not ever again...!\n< Serena >

...Ha... I don't really understand
what's going on, but anyway, the
operation was a success... Is this
really okay?\n< Cecilia >

The fortress seems to be in total chaos.
They're not in any position to bother us
anymore. Let's slip away quietly.\n< Cecilia >

But seriously, what was that thing
earlier?\n< Cecilia >

I once saw it... in the sewers. A black
slime. No... maybe it wasn't slime.\n< Serena >

Catherine-sama mentioned it. Beneath
this city, the lingering thoughts of
numerous lost souls remain. Those
thoughts gather and form a curse...\n< Serena >

That might have been the curse itself.
Why it appeared here and now, I do not
know...\n< Serena >

...Come to think of it, Catherine-sama
did ask me to show them understanding...\n< Serena >

What is that woman talking about? It's
not like we're strangers.\n< Cecilia >

Serena has no obligation to deal with
such things. I blew it away! Serves them
right!\n< Cecilia >

You don't need to worry about such
stories either, Serena. Don't let it
dampen our happy ending.\n< Cecilia >

That's right... I'm sorry, but all I
could do was save this child.\n< Serena >
...\n< Serena >

Let's go home, Splendor. Father and
Mother are surely very angry.\n< Serena >

I might end up crying when they scold
me.\n< Serena >

If that happens, please comfort me
again...\n< Serena >
ストーリー　砦潜入　敗北
シシリア HK01-1
シシリア HK01-1
Ugh!!!\n< Serena >
This monster...!?\n< Serena >
Serena!\n< Cecilia >
Lady Cecilia! Don't mind me!\n< Serena >

It seems this monster is after me...!
Take Splendor and run...!\n< Serena >
Aggh...!\n< Serena >
...!\n< Serena >
...I'm sorry. I'm so sorry!\n< Cecilia >
...\n< Serena >

Is this... the end... in a place like
this...\n< Serena >
It's more anticlimactic than I thought.\n< Serena >
But well, Splendor was saved.\n< Serena >

Though I won't be able to hold that
child in my arms again,\n< Serena >
I'm half satisfied.\n< Serena >
Half is...\n< Serena >
